* "Moj stariji brat **stariji** je od mene." (My older brother is older than me.)
* "Ona je udata za nekog **starijeg** čoveka." (She is married to an older man.)
* "On je **stariji** čovek od mog oca." (He is an older man than my father.)
* "Ona je imala **starijeg** sina." (She had an older son.)
* "Ona je želela da se uda za **starijeg** muškarca." (She wanted to marry an older man.)